        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick, with a matching lid) with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Add the <strong>pepper strips</strong> and <strong>sliced onion</strong> with a big pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Cook for 5 min, then reduce the heat to low and cook for 10-15 min or until softened and caramelised</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1632301720442-x200.jpg",
