            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>On a clean board, chop your<strong> basa fillets</strong> into large bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add 200ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[275ml]</span> [350ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong>, your <strong>softened creamed coconut </strong>and your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> to the pan and stir for 2 min until everything has combined, then gently add the <strong>chopped basa</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
