    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once boiling, reduce to low and cook, covered for 5 min, or until cooked through – this is your <strong>basa, pepper & lemongrass curry</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
