    {
      "instruction": "<p>Stir<strong> half</strong> of the <strong>chopped coriander</strong> through the <strong>basa, pepper & lemongrass curry</strong> and serve over the <strong>lemongrass rice</strong>, discard the <strong>lemongrass</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
